# Comet & Opik Documentation Reference

When writing code related to Comet or Opik, consult the following documentation sources:

## Primary Documentation

- **Comet EM Docs**: https://www.comet.com/docs/v2/
  - Comet Changelog: https://www.comet.com/docs/v2/guides/changelog/
- **Python SDK**: https://www.comet.com/docs/v2/api-and-sdk/python-sdk/
- **Opik Docs**: https://www.comet.com/docs/opik/
  - Opik Changelog: https://www.comet.com/docs/opik/changelog
- **REST API**: https://www.comet.com/docs/v2/api-and-sdk/rest-api/
- **Deployment Docs**: https://cometml.github.io/

## GitHub Repositories

- **Opik Repository**: https://github.com/comet-ml/opik
- **Comet Examples**: https://github.com/comet-ml/comet-examples

## Usage Guidelines

When implementing features or fixing issues:
1. Check the relevant documentation for the latest API patterns
2. Review the changelogs for recent updates that may affect implementation
3. Consult the GitHub repositories for code examples and best practices
